sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Investor
  participant SWS as SWS/Public Gateway
  participant Case as Case Service
  participant AI as AI Service
  participant Doc as Document Service
  participant Orch as Orchestration Service
  participant Mongo as MongoDB
  participant Kafka as Kafka Outbox
  participant Rabbit as RabbitMQ
  Investor->>SWS: Submit CAF and documents
  SWS->>Case: Create/update canonical case
  Case->>AI: Advisory completeness/routing check
  AI-->>Case: Recommendation + confidence
  Case->>Doc: Confirm document metadata
  Doc->>Mongo: Store metadata
  Case->>Mongo: Persist final case
  Case->>Kafka: Append case.submitted.v1
  Case->>Orch: Request approval tracks
  Orch->>Mongo: Create tasks and SLA timers
  Orch->>Kafka: Append task.created.v1
  Orch->>Rabbit: Create delivery jobs
  Case-->>SWS: Universal Case ID and acknowledgement
